            .container
                .columns
                    .column.is-3
                        %p.eyebrow
                            Objectives
                        %h3
                            Revewing Project Goals
                    .column.is-8.is-offset-1
                        %p
                            The Puerto Rico Open's business goals around ticket sales, tourism growth, and brand credibility were only achievable if the site actually worked for the people visiting it. Our goal was to identify where those interests converged and design toward that intersection, building an experience that serves fans, drives attendance, and reflects the cultural significance of the event all at once.
                        .project-goals__graph
                            .columns
                                .column
                                    .graph__business-title
                                        %p Business goals
                                .column
                                    .graph__mutual-title
                                        %p Project goals
                                .column
                                    .graph__user-title
                                        %p User goals
                            .columns.is-vcentered.graph-columns
                                .column
                                    .graph__business-goals
                                        %ul
                                            %li Drive ticket sales
                                            %li Increase tourism
