                        %thead
                            %tr
                                %th Page / Feature
                                %th Priority
                                %th Description
                                %th Goal
                        %tbody
                            %tr
                                %td Homepage
                                %td.phase
                                    %span.p1 P1 — Must Have
                                %td Hero with event dates, ticket CTA, and a live state that adapts between pre-event countdown, tournament week leaderboard, and post-event highlights. Featured player section with Rafa Campos emphasis, El 19 preview, sponsor strip, and news feed.
